Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.98,0:00:13.82,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:9989,13826}I can feel the sunshine on me,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.82,0:00:17.12,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:13826,17121}I think I'll bask in it a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.12,0:00:22.12,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:18122,22126}It's a beginning of a new day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.33,0:00:28.46,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:25338,28466}That's the moment I like the most,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.34,0:00:33.51,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:29342,33513}the one that starts it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.51,0:00:36.84,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:33513,36849}Something lovely is about to happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.84,0:00:40.72,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:36849,40728}I just have a hunch like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.72,0:00:48.40,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:40728,48403}Woom! My reflection the mirror
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:52.28,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:48403,52282}Woom! Looks rather pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.28,0:00:56.03,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:52282,56035}It feels so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.03,0:01:02.87,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:56035,62875}I reach out to the clear blue sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.79,0:01:10.67,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:63793,70675}I'm so excited and filled with hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.46,0:01:15.09,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:71467,75096}Love, work, everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.09,0:01:18.60,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:75096,78600}I want to take these challenges on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.60,0:01:24.89,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:78600,84897}and build myself again.
Comment: 0,0:01:35.11,0:01:35.11,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:95116,95116}Part A
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.84,0:01:53.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:111841,113384}{\i1}I don't want anything…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.96,0:01:57.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:114969,117555}{\i1}You are the only treasure I need.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.22,0:02:02.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:120224,122352}{\i1}Your eyes are my greatest treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.93,0:02:10.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,[title],{TIME:126939,130943}The Final Battle!\NSave Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.90,0:02:14.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:131903,134405}What?! Sister?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.19,0:02:18.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:136199,138951}Asuka Jr. hasn't come home?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.95,0:02:20.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:138951,140119}Is it true?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.66,0:02:23.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:140662,143831}He's been absent for four days already!\NDid he disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.83,0:02:25.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:143831,145375}Where did he go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.37,0:02:26.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:145375,146709}Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.70,0:02:29.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:146709,149087}Right now, the police\Nare looking for him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.58,0:02:33.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:150588,153049}Then he really is missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.63,0:02:37.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:153633,157011}Sister! How is Detective Asuka?\NAsuka's father?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.01,0:02:42.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:157011,162809}Asuka's father is on a top-secret mission\Nright now and we can't contact him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.80,0:02:44.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:162809,164268}Anyway, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.26,0:02:45.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:164268,165895}He'll be fine, everyone…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.64,0:02:50.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:166646,170483}{\i1}I ran for my life\Nfrom the monastery…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.94,0:02:58.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:175947,178950}{\i1}Asuka Jr. didn't come\Nto the place in my warning note.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.95,0:03:05.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:180952,185415}{\i1}He was already missing\Nat that time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.21,0:03:10.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:189210,190253}Takamiya…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.25,0:03:15.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:192255,195842}He probably\Nscrewed up somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.42,0:03:18.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:196426,198845}But still, Asuka is Asuka…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.84,0:03:22.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:198845,202765}I'm sure he is eating and sleeping\Nwhen he needs to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.76,0:03:24.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:202765,204809}He'll pop up sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.68,0:03:28.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:206686,208771}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.18,0:03:31.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:210189,211274}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.11,0:03:37.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:216112,217196}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:57.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:234422,237633}{\i1}It's been four days since I was\Nlocked in the top of this tower…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.93,0:04:08.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:247935,248978}{\i1}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.31,0:04:12.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:250313,252523}{\i1}Why did you hide\Nthe truth from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.60,0:04:17.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:254609,257695}{\i1}Were you enjoying teasing me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.48,0:04:20.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:258488,260656}{\i1}What was I to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.65,0:04:25.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:261657,265620}{\i1}What did you think of me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.96,0:04:36.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:274962,276172}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.17,0:04:39.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:276172,279509}Asuka Jr. didn't show up\Nat the warning note's location…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.05,0:04:41.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:280051,281928}Did he see the warning note?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.92,0:04:43.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:281928,283596}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.59,0:04:44.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:283596,284430}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.43,0:04:45.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:284430,285932}Maju said…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.93,0:04:48.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:285932,288935}No matter how much you search,\Nthe detective won't come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.43,0:04:54.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:289435,294440}Meimi! Does this mean Asuka Jr.\Nwas captured by her and her mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.39,0:05:00.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:295399,300321}{\i1}They're punishing me to get\Ntheir revenge on Mom and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.32,0:05:01.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:300321,301864}{\i1}It's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.69,0:05:03.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:302698,303866}I'm getting him back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.32,0:05:05.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:304325,305034}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.82,0:05:09.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:305827,309330}Oh, Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.87,0:05:12.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:309872,312792}Getting him back?!\NYou mean Asuka Jr.?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.67,0:05:18.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:317672,318798}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.13,0:05:22.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:321133,322468}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.38,0:05:26.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:324387,326931}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.69,0:05:39.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:338693,339777}Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.73,0:05:46.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:341737,346242}If you do that, it's the same\Nas telling him your identity!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.24,0:05:48.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:346242,348995}It means that you'll get caught!\NThen you two will…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.53,0:05:51.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:350538,351956}I'm sorry, Seira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.54,0:05:55.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:352540,355418}I suppose I can't be\NSt. Tail anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.71,0:05:58.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:356711,358004}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.67,0:06:01.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:359672,361340}He's an important person to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.42,0:06:08.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:363426,368306}Even though he may hate me, or I may\Nnot be able to see him, I want him back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.14,0:06:13.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:372143,373769}It's no use trying to stop you, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.14,0:06:17.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:376147,377773}Good luck…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.77,0:06:19.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:377773,379191}Seira…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.19,0:06:21.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:379191,381068}I'll be praying for your safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.66,0:06:35.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:393664,395082}Ruby.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.08,0:06:39.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:396083,399045}Please. This is\Nthe only method I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.84,0:06:46.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:403841,406010}Please deliver this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.47,0:06:58.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:412475,418940}Lord, until now Meimi has\Nnever stolen anything for herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.85,0:07:03.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:419857,423778}But this time… only this time…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.77,0:07:07.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:423778,427782}Please protect Meimi and Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.78,0:07:11.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:427782,431202}May the blessings of God\Nbe with the two of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.01,0:07:32.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:451013,452223}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.72,0:07:34.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:452723,454684}It has something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.35,0:07:39.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:457353,459605}St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.98,0:07:42.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:459981,462566}She's coming here soon, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.27,0:07:46.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:464276,466529}Things are going as we planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:50.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:467071,470741}I hypnotized the police\Nand sent them away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.40,0:07:54.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:471409,474620}No one will come to this\Nmonastery and disturb us, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.62,0:07:56.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:474620,476706}All right.\NEverything is in order here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.50,0:08:03.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:480501,483087}Lucifer's daughter…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.08,0:08:07.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:483087,487133}I want to see you suffering soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.64,0:08:16.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:495641,496684}It's time to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.52,0:08:22.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:499520,502481}How long are you planning\Nto keep me locked up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.48,0:08:24.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:502481,504567}That's obvious!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.56,0:08:26.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:504567,506610}Until Mom says so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.61,0:08:28.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:506610,508070}Don't worry about that. Here…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.65,0:08:29.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:508654,509572}This is for you, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.61,0:08:31.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:510614,511824}{\i1}A warning note?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.41,0:08:42.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:520416,522960}Welcome to my house, St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.46,0:08:47.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:525463,527923}Asuka Jr. is here, isn't he?\NLet him go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.34,0:08:51.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:529341,531886}You're a foolish girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.42,0:08:58.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:532428,538809}Did you seriously think\NI would simply hand him over?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.57,0:09:13.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:551572,553282}What a pretty picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.40,0:09:15.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:554408,555618}{\i1}This is a hallucination.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.61,0:09:17.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:555618,557244}{\i1}But I can't breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.23,0:09:49.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:588234,589693}{\i1}Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.11,0:09:52.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:591112,592863}{\i1}I have to find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.95,0:10:02.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:598953,602248}{\i1}How long is this hallway?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.96,0:10:13.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:607962,613175}Keep running,\Nuntil your heart bursts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.01,0:10:17.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:616011,617680}{\i1}The end…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.68,0:10:20.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:617680,620182}{\i1}I can't find the end of the hallway!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.18,0:10:24.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:622184,624812}{\i1}Where is Asuka Jr.?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.27,0:10:33.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:631277,633195}This thing delivered it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.19,0:10:34.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:633195,634989}She's a stupid thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.98,0:10:37.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:634989,637283}She's deliberately come here\Nto be defeated by Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.66,0:10:45.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:640661,645374}"Tonight I'm going to the monastery\Nto get Asuka Jr. – St. Tail"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.79,0:10:48.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:646792,648502}{\i1}Asuka Jr.?!
