Comment: 0,0:10:56.67,0:10:56.67,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:656677,656677}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.77,0:11:15.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:671775,675988}Give him back.\NGive him back. Give him back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.49,0:11:28.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:687499,688834}How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:36.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:694673,696800}Give him back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.67,0:11:42.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:699678,702765}Why don't you come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.35,0:11:48.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:704350,708229}It's a waste for your talent\Nto be stuck in such a small town.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.60,0:11:52.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:708604,712233}That's how Maju joined me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.35,0:11:55.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:712358,715736}She isn't my real daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.73,0:11:59.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:715736,719657}Why don't you join us and grab\Nall of the treasure in the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.44,0:12:04.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:720449,724328}You can get whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.32,0:12:05.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:724328,725663}Gold…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.74,0:12:08.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:725746,728666}Jewels and art…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.66,0:12:11.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:728666,731043}You can live in luxury.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.54,0:12:14.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:732544,734588}I don't want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.25,0:12:19.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:737258,739510}{\i1}What is she talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.26,0:12:23.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:741262,743430}{\i1}What I want is…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.43,0:12:24.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:743430,744807}Give him back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.43,0:12:27.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:745432,747351}He is my only jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.56,0:12:30.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:749561,750938}Give him back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.68,0:12:35.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:751689,755693}So that boy is\Nyour 100-carat diamond…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.69,0:12:38.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:755693,758612}I guess you aren't very smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.00,0:12:59.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:776005,779925}{\i1}This is a hallucination,\NMeimi. It's not real.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.46,0:13:02.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:780467,782386}{\i1}Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.38,0:13:04.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:783387,784847}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.09,0:13:06.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:785097,786348}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.68,0:13:08.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:786682,788434}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.10,0:13:13.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:792104,793272}This warning note…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.10,0:13:15.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:794106,795357}When did it come?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.56,0:13:17.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:796567,797735}Warning note?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.81,0:13:20.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:798819,800863}Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.86,0:13:23.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:800863,803407}That's a love letter, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.40,0:13:25.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:803407,805200}Boys are so dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.57,0:13:27.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:806577,807786}Love letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.24,0:13:33.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:811248,813167}{\i1}The other notes until now…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.00,0:13:37.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:816003,817004}{\i1}All of them…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.85,0:13:54.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:830851,834313}I want to get caught by you…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.19,0:14:01.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:839193,841779}Don't play with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.82,0:14:04.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:843822,844782}I am…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.49,0:14:08.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:846492,848744}I am not a princess\Nlocked up in a tower!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.41,0:14:13.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:851413,853749}I won't stand by\Nwithout doing anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.91,0:14:16.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:854917,856543}I'm going to get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.54,0:14:18.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:856543,858712}{\i1}Asuka Jr.! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.82,0:14:45.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:883821,885447}Dear Lord…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.03,0:14:48.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:886031,888367}Please protect them…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.41,0:14:55.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:891412,895416}{\i1}God is telling me something…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.29,0:14:59.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:897292,899962}{\i1}Asuka Jr. is in that tower!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.21,0:15:06.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:902214,906802}Butterfly powder is mixing\Nwith my jade dust!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.59,0:15:15.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:912599,915269}Ow! It's so loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.26,0:15:17.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:915269,917020}Now's the time! Grab the keys!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:24.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:921900,924194}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.44,0:15:26.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:925446,926655}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.14,0:15:56.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:953140,956268}You idiot! There used to be\Na bridge to the other tower!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.26,0:15:57.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:956268,957311}But there's nothing there now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.23,0:16:03.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:961231,963150}Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.27,0:16:04.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:963275,964067}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.61,0:16:07.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:965611,967112}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.11,0:16:09.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:967112,969072}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.96,0:16:27.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:984963,987382}Now's not the time to save others!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.06,0:16:42.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1001063,1002689}My silk hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.08,0:17:46.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1063083,1066336}I'm… sorry…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.92,0:17:49.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1067921,1069423}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.42,0:17:50.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1069423,1070966}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.75,0:17:53.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1071758,1073176}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.26,0:17:57.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1075262,1077806}The truth is…\NI'm St. T…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.06,0:18:06.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1085063,1086523}God is…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.89,0:18:09.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1087899,1089985}…watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.90,0:18:20.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1097909,1100621}Surrender and go quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.08,0:18:32.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1110088,1112633}I'm sorry I didn't notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.43,0:18:45.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1122434,1125312}Mom! Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.85,0:18:48.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1126855,1128565}What about our revenge?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.56,0:18:50.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1128565,1130275}It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.85,0:18:54.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1130859,1134696}If only I had met someone\Nlike him 20 years ago…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.69,0:18:55.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1134696,1135364}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.36,0:19:00.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1135364,1140243}If I had someone who\Nloved me no matter what…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.11,0:19:04.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1141119,1144206}Now let's go to the next town\Nand make some money, Maju!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.20,0:19:05.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1144206,1145207}Yes, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.33,0:19:13.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1148335,1153757}From that day, St. Tail\Ndisappeared from Seika City.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.75,0:19:16.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1153757,1156635}After all, she had been caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.88,0:19:19.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1157886,1159304}{\an8}And…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.63,0:19:21.59,saint tail sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1158637,1161598}{\an2\fad(1000,0)\pos(720,1050)}8 years later
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.85,0:19:28.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1166853,1168605}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:32.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1168605,1172025}We were able to save\Nanother lost sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.11,0:19:34.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1173110,1174486}We owe it all to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.23,0:19:36.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1175237,1176947}Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.86,0:19:40.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1177864,1180117}Oh, I shouldn't call you\NJunior anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.11,0:19:42.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1180117,1182953}You're a full-fledged\Nprivate investigator now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.95,0:19:45.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1182953,1185455}– But I'm not used to it yet.\N– Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.45,0:19:49.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1185455,1189584}Asuka! Don't steal work\Nfrom the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.58,0:19:52.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1189584,1192504}He means to protect the peace\Nin Seika City, doesn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.50,0:19:55.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1192504,1195632}Hey, let me get the scoop next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.63,0:19:56.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1195632,1196633}Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.71,0:20:00.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1197718,1200595}After all, St. Tail\Nprotected this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.01,0:20:02.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1201012,1202764}St. Tail…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.76,0:20:04.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1202764,1204683}I wonder where she went…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.68,0:20:05.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1204683,1205559}Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.43,0:20:10.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1208437,1210939}She's in the chapel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.93,0:20:13.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1210939,1213233}You parked illegally, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.23,0:20:15.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1213233,1215736}– What?\N– Wait! Saruwatari!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.74,0:20:21.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1220741,1221700}Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.79,0:20:34.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1228790,1234713}The secret promise they had will\Nbecome an eternal promise one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.67,0:20:39.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1236673,1239551}Yes, that day isn't far off.
