Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.24,0:21:09.91,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1267245,1269915}Let me dream of a melody,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.91,0:21:14.96,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1269915,1274961}'cause something tells me\Nwe won't stay like that for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.96,0:21:22.42,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1274961,1282427}The future is like a rainbow,\Na tunnel of vibrant colors,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.42,0:21:26.76,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1282427,1286765}and I'm stepping right inside of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.10,0:21:37.15,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1294105,1297150}The night after our mysterious date
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.02,0:21:42.15,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1298026,1302155}I get so lonely you wouldn't imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.61,0:21:49.70,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1302614,1309704}Under my eyelids there's only image of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.70,0:21:53.29,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1309704,1313291}I want to remodel this romance
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.41,0:21:56.54,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1313416,1316545}and forget about yesterday already.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.21,0:22:01.00,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1317212,1321007}Let's stop holding back and get carried away.
